text:

title: Post With Code
text:
This is a post with executable code.
We can use Python.

a = 10
b = a**2

We can use the result inside of a \LaTeX snippet.

\begin{aligned}
b & = a^2 \\
b & = 100
\end{aligned}

Or in the main text: With a = 10 the value of a^2 is 100.
